    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Sadly, the current situation with travis-ci has become unbearable. Investigate Linux/macOS (and Windows) options on\r\n- circle-ci\r\n- azure\r\n- potentially also Github Actions, but that seems more work for less benefit currently (no Windows support, very different setup).\r\n\r\nWe currently use [multibuild](https://github.com/matthew-brett/multibuild/) in the [cython-wheels](https://github.com/MacPython/cython-wheels) project, but should also consider [cibuildwheel](https://pypi.org/project/cibuildwheel/).\r\n",
    "closed_at": null,
